Class AbstractIconScheme

    public abstract class AbstractIconScheme
extends AbstractUIScheme<Icon,DockIcon,DockIconBridge>
    This abstract implementation of an UIScheme offers support for transferring values from the DockProperties to the IconManager.
    Author:
    Benjamin Sigg
